    FUTURE SUPPORT

   CullMask Feature for Camera

  cull matrix

Camera resolution


Camera to World Matrix
and World to Camera Matrix


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Back ground Color for the camera.

  Camera Render Order (Priority)
   Camera with the higher Priority will be rendered first.
   Camera wil the lower Priority will be rendered last.

Fov Scaling Algorithm
    HorizontalPlus,
    Anamorphic,
    VerticalMinus,
    Stretch,

    HorizontalPlus is the default, since it is used most frequently in the game industry.